Output demo/demo.gif

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 13
Set Padding 16

# --- Install ---
Sleep 1s
Type "npx @whenlabs/when install"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

# --- when init ---
Sleep 1200ms
Type "when init"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 5s

# --- when doctor ---
Sleep 1200ms
Type "when doctor"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

# --- when status ---
Sleep 1200ms
Type "when status"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 1s
